A '''bo-[[Toad/Legends|toad]]''' was a slow-moving bio-luminescent amphibious animal that could be found on [[U-Tendik]] in the [[Mid Rim/Legends|Mid Rim]]. In [[4 BBY/Legends|4 BBY]], the young [[Rodian/Legends|Rodian]] known as [[Pqweeduk]] came upon some bo-toads while exploring the caves and jungle valleys of his homeworld.

